## Agent 1 — Vonage SMS Transport

**Goal this session:** inbound + outbound Vonage SMS working with persistence and delivery status.

**Paths:**
- [gateway/src/routes/vonage.ts](mdc:gateway/src/routes/vonage.ts)
- [gateway/src/services/vonage.ts](mdc:gateway/src/services/vonage.ts)
- [gateway/src/index.ts](mdc:gateway/src/index.ts)
- [gateway/schema.sql](mdc:gateway/schema.sql)
- [gateway/src/services/db.ts](mdc:gateway/src/services/db.ts)

**Deliver today:**
- Webhook endpoint (inbound) + signature check
- Outbound send function
- Delivery callback handling
- Idempotency guard (no duplicate message writes)

**Done when:**
- You can send an SMS in, get an AI response out, and see statuses in DB/logs.

