## Agent 2 — Scheduling Reliability

**Goal this session:** booking flows become deterministic and safe.

**Paths:**
- [agents/scheduling/main.py](mdc:agents/scheduling/main.py)
- [agents/shared/db.py](mdc:agents/shared/db.py)
- [agents/shared/types.py](mdc:agents/shared/types.py)

**Deliver today:**
- Stronger intent parsing for book/reschedule/cancel/check
- Conflict detection + alternate slot suggestion
- Confirmation gates for cancel/reschedule
- Structured action output (action, status, next_prompt)

**Done when:**
